Package com.bsuir.kirillpastukhou.webappfilms.command

Interface Command

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddCommentCommand, AddFilmCommand, AddToCartCommand, BuyFilmsCommand, DeleteCommentCommand, DeleteFilmCommand, DeleteFromCartCommand, DislikeCommand, EditCommentCommand, EditFilmCommand, EditSaleCommand, LikeCommand, LogoutCommand, RegistrationCommand, ShowEditCommentCommand, ShowEditFilmCommand, ShowEditSaleCommand, SignInCommand, ToAdminCommand, ToCartCommand, ToFilmCommand, ToMainCommand, ToRegistrationCommand, ToSignInCommand, ToUserCommand, UnknownCommand
public interface Command
Interface for implementing command classes. Each command class must implement this interface and provide an implementation for the execute method, which executes the specific command logic.

  • Method Details

    • execute

      String execute(jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request) throws CommandException
      Executes the command logic based on the provided HttpServletRequest. The method takes the request as a parameter and returns a string result. Implementations of this method should handle the command logic and return the result or an appropriate error message.
      Parameters:
      request - The HttpServletRequest object representing the current request
      Returns:
      A string result of the command execution
      Throws:
      CommandException - if there is an error executing the command
